reviewText:
PLOT: episodes from the 1950s tv series.

1. a woman heads a gang of robbers but a dress she is fixated on becomes a robbery focus. 2. 3 killers use scissors to terrorize and kill as they rob. 3. teenagers terrorize the police 4. eye glasses are the only clue to a clever robbery scheme. cheap sets, bad acting, but still fun cheesy.
Entertaining, but contrary to its claims, bears little resemblance to hisorical fact,
